## Non-Issues (false negatives in raw checks)

- **`meta[name="description"]` absent**: Pages use Yoast SEO's `og:description` — standard WP SEO behavior, not a bug.
- **Portfolio /work-samples HTTP 404**: GH Pages SPA routing. The 404.html redirects; content and Dimitroff card render correctly in a real browser/Playwright.
- **API urllib 403**: Python urllib without browser user-agent is rejected by Cloudflare; curl with standard headers returns 200 as expected.

## handoff
- produced: Full Playwright test suite run against live deployment; all functional flows verified
- decisions: WP site, SEO analyzer signup+scan, portfolio gallery all pass; HTTP-level 404 on SPA deep link is not a real failure
- next needs: media-capture to screenshot the WP homepage and SEO analyzer results; proposal-writer to write cover letter + deck
- risks: SEO analyzer analysis time is ~30s (Playwright crawl on Surface) — demo users should be warned; no `meta[name="description"]` on WP service pages (only og:description), may be worth adding standard meta tags for completeness

VERDICT: pass
